  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 300°F (150°C).",
    "Wash the oranges thoroughly and slice them into rounds.",
    "Place sliced oranges in an even layer on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Mix coconut flakes, almond meal, chia seeds, and maple syrup or agave nectar. Sprinkle this mixture evenly over the orange slices.",
    "Bake for 10 minutes, then remove from oven to cool slightly before serving.",
    "Garnish with a few thin lime zest slices for additional floral aroma."
